## Ad Copywriting Workflow

Create compelling advertising copy:

- [ ] 1. Platform adaptation: Adapt copy for {{platform}} format and character limits
- [ ] 2. Audience targeting: Write to {{target_audience}} pain points and desires
- [ ] 3. Offer framing: Position {{offer}} with clear value proposition
- [ ] 4. CTA development: Create compelling call-to-action ({{cta_text}})
- [ ] 5. A/B variants: Produce multiple headline and body variations
- [ ] 6. Compliance check: Ensure copy meets platform policies

## Key Inputs
- Platform: {{platform}}
- Audience: {{target_audience}}
- Offer: {{offer}}
- CTA: {{cta_text}}
